.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

Color: lavender, light-blue, apricot, blood-red, emerald
Nationality: malaysian, argentine, french, chinese, indian
Beverage: mirinda, fanta, soy-milk, 7up, almond-milk
Cigar: lavendermaster, oliveros, swisher, cain, chaman
Pet: turtle, frog, rat, chinchilla, rabbit
1. Nationality:malaysian == Color:apricot
2. Nationality:swedish == Pet:rat
3. Nationality:argentine == Beverage:7up
4. Color:light-blue is on the left of Color:blood-red
5. Color:light-blue == Beverage:fanta
6. Cigar:swisher == Pet:frog
7. Color:emerald == Cigar:oliveros
8. Beverage:soy-milk is in the middle
9. Nationality:chinese is on the far left
10. Cigar:chaman is on the left or right of Pet:turtle
11. Pet:rabbits is on the left or right of Cigar:oliveros
12. Cigar:lavendermaster == Beverage:mirinda
13. Nationality:french == Cigar:cain
14. Nationality:chinese is on the left or right of Color:lavender
15. Cigar:chaman is on the left or right of Beverage:almond-milk

